the whole bunch.

1329
01:25:11,193 --> 01:25:13,456
Now I’m telling you
the truth.

1330
01:25:13,456 --> 01:25:16,328
You can ask
my brother.

1331
01:25:16,328 --> 01:25:17,982
Look, I’m not saying
Jewel was lying to you.

1332
01:25:17,982 --> 01:25:19,288
