with the skates?

1463
01:36:19,861 --> 01:36:21,427
Yeah, sure.

1464
01:36:21,427 --> 01:36:22,689
I enjoyed meeting you.

1465
01:36:22,689 --> 01:36:24,779
Yeah.
Nice meeting you.

1466
01:36:26,432 --> 01:36:27,651
